---
/* /en/direttivo — traduzione EN (Fase 1b). Revisione Brunella Bonapace in corso. */

import PaginaIstituzionale from '../../components/PaginaIstituzionale.astro';

const direttivo = [
  { nome: 'Diego Magnoni', carica: 'Presidente' },
  { nome: 'Simone Pangrazzi', carica: 'Vice Presidente' },
  { nome: 'Milena Comini', carica: 'Vice Presidente' },
  { nome: 'Cristian Bresadola', carica: 'Segretario-Tesoriere' },
  { nome: 'Monica Valentinotti', carica: 'Consigliere' },
  { nome: 'Michele Gentilini', carica: 'Consigliere' },
  { nome: 'Andrea Daprà', carica: 'Consigliere' },
  { nome: 'Michele Corradini', carica: 'Consigliere' },
];
---
<PaginaIstituzionale lang="en" ogImage="/og/og-direttivo.jpg"
  occhiello="The Association"
  titolo="The Board"
  intro="The people who lead El Brenz, elected by the Members' Assembly."
  metaDescription="The Board of the El Brenz Association: president, vice-presidents, secretary and councillors elected by the Members' Assembly."
>
  <h2
    class="text-2xl md:text-3xl text-[#1E2E26] font-medium leading-tight m-0 mb-8"
    style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;"
  >
    The Board currently in office
  </h2>

  <ul class="list-none m-0 mb-6 p-0 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
    {direttivo.map((m) => (
      <li class="bg-white border border-[#E5DFCF] px-6 py-5">
        <p
          class="text-[11px] tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-[#C8923E] m-0 mb-1.5"
          style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;"
        >
          {m.carica}
        </p>
        <p
          class="text-xl text-[#1E2E26] font-medium leading-tight m-0"
          style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;"
        >
          {m.nome}
        </p>
      </li>
    ))}
  </ul>

  <p
    class="text-sm text-[#0F0F0F]/60 leading-relaxed m-0 mb-12"
    style="font-family: 'Source Serif 4', Georgia, serif;"
  >
    Profiles of the members, the faces and stories of the people who carry the
    association forward, will follow soon.
  </p>

  <div class="prosa-istituzionale">
    <h2>The bodies of the Association</h2>
    <p>
      As laid down in the Statute (art. 8), the bodies of the Association are the
      <strong>Members' Assembly</strong> (the sovereign body), the
      <strong>Board</strong>, the <strong>President</strong> and two
      <strong>Auditors</strong>.
    </p>
    <p>
      The Board (art. 13) is made up of at least four councillors, joined by the
      President, two Vice-Presidents representing the different valleys, and the
      Secretary/Treasurer, all elected by the ordinary Assembly. It remains in
      office for three years and is re-eligible.
    </p>
    <p>
      The Board is supported by the youth group, the
      <strong>Gruppo Giovani</strong> (the <em>Joveni</em>, the young ones), made
      up of all members under thirty, who elect a representative from among
      themselves.
    </p>
  </div>
</PaginaIstituzionale>
